.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-4-14::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: november, july, january, may, march, february, december
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: adventure, epic, horror, martial-arts, thriller, western, zombie
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: badminton, biathlon, rowing, rugby, skiing, surfing, swimming
 1. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
 2. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in may is the person who's sport is swimming##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in february is in the middle##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in may##3
 6. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 7. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 8. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in november##3
 9. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
10. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
11. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far left or far right##3
12. the person watching horror movies is the person who's sport is skiing##1
13. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
14. the person watching martial-arts movies is in an even position##4
15. the person watching western movies is the person who's birthday is in january##1
16. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
17. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left or right of the person watching zombie movies##3
18. the person who's sport is rowing is the person watching epic movies##1
19. the person who's birthday is in july is the person watching martial-arts movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2       |     3     |       4        |     5     |     6     |    7     |
| Birthday           | november | july | december    | february | may    | january | march |
| Movie-Genre   | horror | martial-arts | thriller  | zombie         | adventure | western   | epic     |
| Sport         | skiing | surfing      | badminton | biathlon       | swimming  | rugby     | rowing   |

