.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-4-15::.
There 7 different types of food: artichoke, carrot, lemon, nectarine, pineapple, plum, pumpkin
The people have 7 different jobs:  librarian, journalist, police-officer, dressmaker, designer, entrepreneur, musician
7 different pets are kept: chinchilla, goat, guinea-pig, hamster, mouse, rabbit, rat
 1. the person eating plum is on the far left##1
 2. the librarian is on the left or right of the owner of the goat##3
 3. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 4. the person eating nectarine is in an even position##4
 5. the person eating artichoke is in an even position##4
 6. the person eating pumpkin is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 7. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the owner of the rat is on the left of the designer##1
 9. the entrepreneur is on the right of the police-officer##1
10. the person eating lemon is on the right of the person eating nectarine##1
11. the person eating pumpkin is on the left or right of the entrepreneur##3
12. the person eating carrot is in an odd position##4
13. the owner of the rabbit is between the librarian and the owner of the chinchilla##2
14. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the designer##1
15. the person eating pineapple is in an even position##4
16. the journalist is on the left or right of the person eating artichoke##3
17. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1
18. the musician is the owner of the goat##1
19. the person eating lemon is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3    |     4      |     5     |     6      |     7      |
| Food          | plum    | pineapple  | pumpkin | artichoke  | carrot    | nectarine  | lemon      |
| Job   | musician | librarian | police-officer  | entrepreneur  | journalist | designer | dressmaker     |
| Pet           | goat    | hamster    | rabbit  | chinchilla | rat       | mouse      | guinea-pig |

