.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-4-16::.
There 7 different types of food: carrot, cherry, grapefruit, kale, onion, pumpkin, spinach
The people have 7 different hobbies: camping, collecting, drawing, filmmaking, fishing, rock-climbing, skydiving
City: liverpool, marseilles, venice, london, miami, hamburg, boston
 1. the person eating onion is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 2. the person eating grapefruit is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is camping##3
 3. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person eating spinach##1
 4. the person eating cherry is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the person traveling to liverpool is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 6. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
 7. the person eating pumpkin is the person traveling to boston##1
 8. the person traveling to marseilles is on the far right##1
 9. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person eating carrot##1
10. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is between the person who's hobby is collecting and the person eating pumpkin##2
11. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far left or far right##3
12. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left or right of the person eating cherry##3
13. the person eating kale is in an odd position##4
14. the person eating onion is on the left of the person traveling to london##1
15. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
16. the person traveling to boston is on the far left or far right##3
17. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left or right of the person traveling to miami##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |      3      |     4      |     5     |     6      |    7    |
| Food          | pumpkin | onion         | kale        | carrot     | spinach   | grapefruit | cherry  |
| Hobby         | drawing | rock-climbing | collecting  | filmmaking | skydiving | fishing    | camping |
| City   | boston     | venice      | london | miami    | liverpool | hamburg    | marseilles  |

