The people prefer 7 different types of sport: basketball, cycling, parkour, rowing, soccer, swimming, volleyball
The people use 7 different means of transport: airplane, bike, boat, bus, helicopter, ship, taxi
 1. the person driving the helicopter is in an odd position##4
 2. the victorian house is the person who's sport is soccer##1
 3. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3
 4. the person driving the taxi is on the far right##1
 5. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
 6. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
 7. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left or right of the person driving the bus##3
 8. the tower house is on the left or right of the ranch-style house##3
 9. the person driving the ship is on the left of the colonial house##1
10. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the person driving the ship##3
11. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
12. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the tower house##1
13. the person driving the airplane is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3
14. the ranch-style house is the person who's sport is swimming##1
15. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
16. the wooden house is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
17. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
18. the person driving the bike is the person who's sport is cycling##1

.:: Answer ::.
