7 different games are played: snooker, mah-jongg, canasta, scrabble, go, monopoly, domino
7 different pets are kept: chinchilla, ferret, frog, goat, hedgehog, mouse, snake
 1. the owner of the snake is on the left or right of the person playing canasta##3
 2. the owner of the snake is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3
 3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is between the owner of the chinchilla and the person playing canasta##2
 4. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
 5. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left or right of the person playing domino##3
 6. the person playing mah-jongg is on the far right##1
 7. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is baking##3
 9. the owner of the goat is on the far right##1
10. the person playing snooker is the owner of the snake##1
11. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left or right of the person playing go##3
12. the owner of the hedgehog is the person who's hobby is baking##1
13. the owner of the snake is in an even position##4
14. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
15. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left or right of the owner of the chinchilla##3
16. the owner of the frog is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
17. the person who's hobby is camping is the person playing scrabble##1
18. the person playing canasta is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
19. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the person playing snooker##1

.:: Answer ::.
