The people use 7 different means of transport: bike, boat, jet-ski, scooter, ship, subway, tram
 1. the person who growstulip is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
 2. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left or right of the person driving the tram##3
 3. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
 4. the person who growsrose is in an odd position##4
 5. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left or right of the person driving the ship##3
 6. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 7. the person who growsiris is on the far right##1
 8. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
 9. the person driving the tram is the person who growsdaffodil##1
10. the person who's sport is handball is on the left or right of the person who growsrose##3
11. the person who's sport is rugby is the person driving the jet-ski##1
12. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
13. the person who's sport is golf is on the far left or far right##3
14. the person who growsamaryllis is in the middle##1
15. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##3
16. the person driving the jet-ski is between the person who growsamaryllis and the person who growstulip##2
17. the person who's sport is handball is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
18. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the person who growsazalea##3

