.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-4-20::.
The people use 7 different means of transport: subway, van, snowmobile, trike, ship, bike, skateboard
The people have 7 different jobs:  architect, bartender, doctor, entrepreneur, lawyer, nurse, software-developer
7 different pets are kept: cat, fish, frog, hamster, horse, rat, snake
 1. the architect is on the left of the doctor##1
 2. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far right##1
 3. the person driving the skateboard is on the left or right of the person driving the bike##3
 4. the software-developer is the owner of the cat##1
 5. the person driving the ship is on the left or right of the person driving the van##3
 6. the owner of the hamster is the entrepreneur##1
 7. the person driving the ship is on the left of the software-developer##1
 8. the owner of the fish is the person driving the snowmobile##1
 9. the owner of the rat is the architect##1
10. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the bartender##3
11. the person driving the van is on the left of the entrepreneur##1
12. the person driving the trike is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
13. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the person driving the bike##3
14. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the entrepreneur##3
15. the owner of the hamster is the person driving the bike##1
16. the owner of the rat is on the left or right of the person driving the skateboard##3
17. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the nurse##3
18. the architect is in an odd position##4
19. the entrepreneur is on the left or right of the person driving the van##3
20. the owner of the frog is between the owner of the hamster and the architect##2
21. the person driving the trike is the architect##1
22. the owner of the snake is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |         2          |      3       |     4     |     5     |      6      |    7    |
| Transport   | ship | van         | bike    | skateboard   | trike   | subway | snowmobile |
| Job     | nurse      | software-developer | entrepreneur | bartender | architect | doctor      | lawyer  |
| Pet     | horse      | cat                | hamster      | frog      | rat       | snake       | fish    |

 